215
00:10:48.355 --> 00:10:51.645
that New Zealand's political system has few checks on the

216
00:10:51.645 --> 00:10:53.485
power of ministers and cabinet compared

217
00:10:53.665 --> 00:10:55.605
to most well-functioning democracies.

218
00:10:56.865 --> 00:10:59.085
The amendment bill further strengthens the power

219
00:10:59.085 --> 00:11:02.645
of the executive over the publicly funded health sector in

220
00:11:02.645 --> 00:11:05.605
